Version 0.0.6 - Released 2008/10/05
===================================

FULL CHANGES
------------

 - Added Horde configuration.

 - Improved general configuration settings.

SHORT CHANGES
-------------

p@rdalys-0.0.6 is an intermediate release that provides many fixes and
improvements but does not yet deliver the complete Kolab server
configuration.


